                                <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                                    Floating shelves are one of the best DIY upgrades you can add to your home. They
                                    look modern, save space, and provide a stylish way to display decor, books, plants,
                                    or kitchen items. The best part is that you don’t need expert skills to get great
